Package: capR
Type: Package
Title: R-Hosted CAP-Digest Runtime
Version: 1.1.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Yihui", "Xia", email = "xiayh0107@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Builds deterministic, policy-bounded CAP-Digest artifacts from R
    objects through an open adapter runtime. The initial stable conformance
    target is the CAP-Digest version 1.0 table fixture surface.
